title: Witcher Novels
description: Here be ALL books on the Witcher, translated into English, of course! Feast yer eyes on the entire, complete collection, containing ALL stories ever written about the famous Witcher, Geralt of Rivia! Ye shall find both professionally translated books and commercially available for purchase in English, like the first 2 to be worked upon (blood of elves + the sword of destiny) and non professional, amateur translations of ALL THE REST, that have yet to show up in the market! Only ONE is absent, but that title is not entirely about the Witcher, it contains other works/short stories of the author, so it doesn't count anyway. Good reading me hearties, yarr!
